high_descs: Turn left then go to the side table on the bed
Pick up the cd on the side table
Turn left move backwards face the drawer of the side table
Open the drawer and put in the cd then close the drawer
Move forward facing the side table
Pick up the cd
Turn back and move backwards facing the drawer
Open the drawer and put in the cd then close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put the two cd in the drawer

high_descs: Walk over to the wooden nightstand next to the bed behind you.
Pick up the leftmost disc off of the nightstand.
Turn around and walk forward then turn back around to face the nightstand.
Open the lower drawer of the nightstand and put the disc inside, then close the drawer.
Turn right and walk over to the bed, then turn left and walk up to the nightstand.
Pick up the disc off of the nightstand.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and take a step forward, turn right again to face the nightstand.
Open the lower drawer of the nightstand and put the disc inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two discs into the drawer of a nightstand.

high_descs: Turn around go forward and then left to face the night stand with a clock and discs on it.
Pick the disc up from the left side of the night stand.
Move back and face the bottom drawer of the night stand.
Put the disc in the bottom drawer of the night stand.
Move forward and face the top of the night stand.
Pick the disc up from the night stand.
Move back and face the bottom drawer of the night stand.
Put the disc in the night stand.
anns.task_desc: Put two discs in a night stand.
